LVMH to Open Luxury Sites to Public on October Weekend, JDD Says

-- B y   A n d r e w   R o b e r t s
-- 
2011-06-05T10:30:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-05/lvmh-to-open-luxury-sites-to-public-on-october-weekend-jdd-says.html
LVMH Moet Hennessy Louis Vuitton SA (MC) ,
the world’s largest luxury-goods maker, will hold an open house
at more than 25 of its brands on the weekend of Oct. 15-16 to
showcase their craftsmanship and know-how, Antoine Arnault told
Le Journal du Dimanche in an  interview .  Members of the public will be able to visit sites including
Dior’s atelier in Paris, Louis Vuitton’s workshops in Asnières
and Glenmorangie’s distilleries in Scotland, said Berluti Chief
Executive Officer Arnault, according to the French newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Andrew Roberts  in Paris at 
 aroberts36@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
